<li><strong>Doors open at 10 am. The performance begins at 10:30 am; please plan your arrival time accordingly. Brunch will be served mid-performance at 11:30 am.</strong></li>
<li>This performance involves moving between multiple outdoor locations which may include crossing gravel, grassy, or uneven terrain. Dress for weather conditions, with appropriate footwear for periods of standing or walking. Brunch will be served under a shelter with tables and seating provided.</li>
<li>This program runs rain or shine. A rain location at the museum has been identified in the event of inclement weather.</li>
